---
title: "Placeholder Component"
---

# Placeholder

A light-purple box with a dark-purple outline and a centered label. Used to stand in for layout elements (header, footer, announcement banner) while their real implementations are under construction. Dark mode swaps the two purples.

## Properties

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `name` | `string` | (required) | The label text rendered inside the placeholder |
| `class` | `string` | — | Optional extra class applied to the root element, used by the layout wrappers (`AnnouncementBannerPlaceholder`, `HeaderPlaceholder`, `FooterPlaceholder`) to set dimensions and positioning |

