## Layout wrappers

The primitive is consumed by three thin wrappers that take care of positioning and sizing with Hugo-identical dimensions. All three are rendered automatically by `BaseLayout`, so you can see them right now on this page:

- **`AnnouncementBannerPlaceholder`** — fixed to the top, 30px tall, above the header.
- **`HeaderPlaceholder`** — fixed below the banner, 60px tall below 992px and 130px tall at 992px and up.
- **`FooterPlaceholder`** — in normal flow at the bottom of the page, with Hugo-matching responsive vertical padding.

